Parameters.HelpText:
JSON object called schema, who defines the layout of the JSON input object

```
{
   "type":"object",
   "properties":{
      "name":{
         "type":"string",
         "minimum":1
      },
      "age":{
         "type":"number",
         "minimum":1
      }
   },
   "additionalProperties":false,
   "required":[
      "name",
      "age"
   ]
}
```
